description:
On today’s show, Emily is bringing you a mash-up all about dating – because what better way to prepare for the summer than with tips & tricks for getting back in the field.

She gives you just the inspiration you need to embrace the dating game, how to reframe rejection, as well as confidence boosters for the first date. Plus, where to start when you’re brand new to the dating apps.

Thank you for supporting our sponsors who help keep the show FREE: Boston Scientific, pjur Lube, Good Vibrations, SiriusXM, Womanizer. 

Follow Emily on all social: @sexwithemily

For even more sex talk, tips, & tricks visit sexwithemily.com
